<h4><a href="https://www.yicai.com/news/100851131.html">华为或重启 4G 手机生产，最快明年上半年上市</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1381417" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/p30-pro-cam-hero-web.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="1000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/p30-pro-cam-hero-web.jpg 1500w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/p30-pro-cam-hero-web-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/p30-pro-cam-hero-web-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/p30-pro-cam-hero-web-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" /></p>
<p>此前有消息称，华为正在积极向供应商订购 4G 智能手机以及相关终端零部件，部分组件制造商已收到通知，将在本月恢复购买主板和其他部件产品。</p>
<p>《第一财经》援引华为供应链知情人士称，4G 新的手机订单已经陆续开始备货：「目前都是小批量滚动下单，具体订单量还没有办法预估。」</p>
<p>报道称，按照市场订单出货节奏，现阶段的手机订单成品预计明年上半年上市。从时间点判断，最快将会在一季度。</p>
<p>华为方面则对上述消息不予回应。</p>
<h4><a href="https://time.com/collection/best-inventions-2020/">《时代》发布年度最佳发明排行榜</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1381394" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/best-inventions-2020-01.jpg" alt="" width="2400" height="1350" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/best-inventions-2020-01.jpg 2400w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/best-inventions-2020-01-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/best-inventions-2020-01-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/best-inventions-2020-01-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2400px) 100vw, 2400px" /></p>
<p>《时代（TIME）》杂志公布了 2020 年度最佳发明排行榜，一共有 100 样产品上榜，并分为「无障碍」「人工智能」「消费电子」「设计」「教育」等多个类别。</p>
<p>其中，微软的 Surface Duo、Insta360 One R、《动物之森》、PS5、Nike Air Zoom Alphafly Next% 等产品均有上榜。<a href="https://time.com/collection/best-inventions-2020/">完整列表</a>如下：</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1381395" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/list.jpg" alt="" width="2658" height="829" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/list.jpg 2658w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/list-360x112.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/list-768x240.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/list-1024x319.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2658px) 100vw, 2658px" /></p>
<h4><a href="https://www.foxnews.com/health/redfield-projects-covid-19-vaccine-to-be-rolled-out-by-end-of-the-second-week-in-december">美疾控中心：疫苗或于 12 月中推出</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1381396" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5e6a21cda3101282065beb67.jpeg" alt="" width="1199" height="800" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5e6a21cda3101282065beb67.jpeg 1199w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5e6a21cda3101282065beb67-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5e6a21cda3101282065beb67-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5e6a21cda3101282065beb67-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1199px) 100vw, 1199px" /></p>
<p>美国疾控中心主任 Robert Redfield 告知 Fox News，一款新冠疫苗大概会在 12 月第二周结束时在美国推出。</p>
<p>Redfield 表示，疫苗最初将「分级式」地供应，优先度最高的为养老院居民，然后到医护人员和部分高风险感染个人。</p>
<h4>最新疫情数字</h4>
<p><strong>国内（不含港澳台）</strong>：11 月 24 日，新增确诊病例 5 例，均为境外输入病例（上海 2 例，福建 1 例，广东 1 例，陕西 1 例）；无新增死亡病例；新增疑似病例 1 例，为本土病例（在内蒙古）。</p>
<p><strong>香港</strong>：11 月 23 日新增 80 例确诊病例，其中 11 例为输入性病例。香港累计报告确诊病例达 5781 例。</p>
<p><strong>海外</strong>：截至 11 月 25 日 7 时，海外累计确诊病例 59,780,787 例，累计死亡 1,404,905 例，累计治愈 41,021,895 例。</p>
<h4><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293888" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/keji.png" alt="" width="1715" height="300" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/keji.png 1715w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/keji-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/keji-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/keji-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1715px) 100vw, 1715px" /></h4>
<h4><a href="https://hypebeast.cn/2020/11/capcom-retro-station-street-fighter-mega-man-console">CAPCOM 推出迷你复古游戏街机</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1381397" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/capcom-retro-station-street-fighter-mega-man-console-1.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="800" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/capcom-retro-station-street-fighter-mega-man-console-1.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/capcom-retro-station-street-fighter-mega-man-console-1-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/capcom-retro-station-street-fighter-mega-man-console-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/capcom-retro-station-street-fighter-mega-man-console-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>Hypebeast 消息，日本游戏开发商 CAPCOM 推出迷你复古游戏街机 Retro Station，搭载 8 英寸屏幕和六个按钮及一个操纵杆，配有 HDMI 接口和耳机插孔。</p>
<p>用户可在这款游戏机上玩《街头霸王》和《洛克人》等经典游戏。Retro Station 预计于 12 月 1 日在日本亚马逊发售。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.feng.com/post/13130352">OPPO Reno5 5G 现身跑分平台</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1381398" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/204516fct3ushgmbi85n8g.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="300" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/204516fct3ushgmbi85n8g.jpg 600w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/204516fct3ushgmbi85n8g-360x180.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></p>
<p>威锋网消息， OPPO Reno5 系列现身 Geekbench。 根据信息显示，型号为 OPPO PEGM00 的设备搭载骁龙 765G 芯片，而第二款型号为 OPPO PDST00 的手机则采用了联发科的天玑 1000+ 芯片。</p>
<p>尽管使用不同的芯片，但它们都具有 8GB RAM 并运行 Android 11（ColorOS 11）操作系统。 跑分方面，前者在单核和多核测试中分别获得 616 分和 1817 分。另一方面，后者分别获得 725 分和 3000 分。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293889" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://36kr.com/p/982068411272578">小米公布第三季度财报</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1381399" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16024743363731700.jpg" alt="" width="2500" height="1667" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16024743363731700.jpg 2500w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16024743363731700-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16024743363731700-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16024743363731700-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2500px) 100vw, 2500px" /></p>
<p>36kr 消息，小米公布第三季度财报。数据显示，小米 Q3 营收 721.6 亿元人民币，高于市场预估的 700.20 亿元，同比增长 34.5%，环比增长 34.8%；非国际财务报告准则下，经调整净利润为 41.3 亿元，同比增长 18.9%。</p>
<p>华为手机市场份额收缩叠加疫情的双重因素，小米得到了增长的机会。本季度，小米的总收入和经调整净利润都创下单季历史新高。</p>
<p>从细分业务来看，小米 Q3 智能手机部分收入为 476 亿元，同比增长 47.5%；IoT 与生活消费产品部分的收入 181 亿元，同比增长 16.1%；互联网服务收入 58 亿元，同比增长 8.7%。</p>
<h4><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/YNvlQacdGBhGiP4w2FWGLg">消息称字节跳动在研发多款教育硬件</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1381400" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/bytedance-dali-smart-lamp.jpg" alt="" width="1390" height="835" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/bytedance-dali-smart-lamp.jpg 1390w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/bytedance-dali-smart-lamp-360x216.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/bytedance-dali-smart-lamp-768x461.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/bytedance-dali-smart-lamp-1024x615.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1390px) 100vw, 1390px" /></p>
<p>《晚点 LatePose》消息，字节跳动过去曾通过旗下教育品牌「大力教育」发布了「大力智能作业灯」。</p>
<p>报道称，除台灯外，字节跳动还在研发多款教育硬件，其中包括教育平板，发布时间暂时还未确定；有口袋学习打印机，已从工厂下线，还未推向市场；还有儿童早教机、词典笔等，已经启动早期调研。</p>
<p>相较于网易有道、猿辅导、作业帮等互联网教育公司，字节跳动目前布局的硬件品类最多，投入研发资源最重。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.engadget.com/hugo-award-video-games-220425979.html">2021 年「雨果奖」将设立「最佳游戏奖」</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1381401" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DctMKib3EJXqHr9s6RPuQn.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="420" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DctMKib3EJXqHr9s6RPuQn.jpg 800w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DctMKib3EJXqHr9s6RPuQn-360x189.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DctMKib3EJXqHr9s6RPuQn-768x403.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></p>
<p>Engadget 消息，针对科幻文学的「雨果奖」将于 2021 年特别设立「最佳游戏奖」。</p>
<p>第 79 届世界科幻大会的联合主席 Collette Fozard 在 Twitter 上分享了该消息，并解释称，今年以来，我们花在玩游戏上的时间远超预期，该奖项为粉丝提供了一个表彰好游戏的机会。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357461" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="http://m.news.cctv.com/2020/11/24/ARTIKaIdRYdsXkReQpymYgO8201124.shtml">国际航协拟推出数字健康通行证</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1381402" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/photo-1555685460-1d9cf532761b.jpeg" alt="" width="1080" height="584" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/photo-1555685460-1d9cf532761b.jpeg 1080w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/photo-1555685460-1d9cf532761b-360x195.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/photo-1555685460-1d9cf532761b-768x415.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/photo-1555685460-1d9cf532761b-1024x554.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px" /></p>
<p>央视消息，国际航空运输协会表示，正在开发多款手机应用，协助航空旅客了解各目的地新冠肺炎疫情限制措施，并与航空公司或政府共享个人病毒检测或疫苗接种信息。</p>
<p>这些手机应用将构成「国际航协旅行通行证」数字平台，拟于今年年底前试点推出，计划于明年第一季度正式推出，以推动安全旅行。</p>
<h4><a href="https://hypebeast.cn/2020/11/uniqlo-and-jw-anderson-release-info">优衣库和 JW ANDERSON 合作推出节日系列</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1381403" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uniqlo-and-jw-anderson-release-info-03.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="853" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uniqlo-and-jw-anderson-release-info-03.jpg 1280w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uniqlo-and-jw-anderson-release-info-03-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uniqlo-and-jw-anderson-release-info-03-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/uniqlo-and-jw-anderson-release-info-03-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /></p>
<p>Hypebeast 消息，优衣库宣布再和 JW ANDERSON 合作，以「英国乡村温馨小屋」为主题，推出首个 UNIQLO and JW ANDERSON 节日合作系列。</p>
<p>该系列融入了优衣库的 HEATTECH 保暖面料，包括多款保暖配饰单品，如针织帽、围脖、手套和袜子。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.theverge.com/21612698/mandalorian-cookie-macarons-the-child-williams-sonoma-star-wars-price">「Baby Yoda」吃的同款马卡龙发售</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1381404" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/nevarro-nummies-macarons-3-c.jpg" alt="" width="574" height="410" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/nevarro-nummies-macarons-3-c.jpg 574w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/nevarro-nummies-macarons-3-c-360x257.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 574px) 100vw, 574px" /></p>
<p>The Verge 消息，《曼达洛人》第二季中「Baby Yoda」所吃的蓝色马卡龙「Nevarro Nummies」已经可在 Williams Sonoma 买到。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1381405" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/img1o.jpg" alt="" width="710" height="710" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/img1o.jpg 710w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/img1o-360x360.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 710px) 100vw, 710px" /></p>
<p>12 只装的 Nevarro Nummies 价格为 49.95 美元（ 约人民币 327 元）。</p>
<h4><a href="https://techcrunch.com/2020/11/23/queens-gambit-viewership/">《后翼弃兵》成 Netflix 史上最受欢迎迷你剧</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1381406" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Queens-Gambit-Chess-Player-Review.jpg" alt="" width="1998" height="1332" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Queens-Gambit-Chess-Player-Review.jpg 1998w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Queens-Gambit-Chess-Player-Review-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Queens-Gambit-Chess-Player-Review-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Queens-Gambit-Chess-Player-Review-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1998px) 100vw, 1998px" /></p>
<p>TechCrunch 消息，《后翼弃兵》在上线 28 天后，以 6200 万家庭播放成为 Netflix 史上最多人观看的迷你剧。如进行跨类别对比，该剧的播放则仍低于电视剧《猎魔人》（7600 万播放）和纪录片《养虎为患》（6400 万播放）。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293890" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E5%B0%86%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%A0%81%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%98%E9%80%9A%E8%A1%8C%E5%94%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%87%AD%E8%AF%81%23&amp;Refer=top">不得将健康码作为人员通行唯一凭证</a></h4>
<p>国办发文指出，各地不得将「健康码」作为人员通行的唯一凭证，对老年人等群体可采取凭有效身份证件登记、持纸质证明通行、出示「通信行程卡」作为辅助行程证明等替代措施。有条件的地区和场所要为不使用智能手机的老年人设立「无健康码通道」，做好服务引导和健康核验。</p>
<p>网友：「文件有了，下一步好好落实基层才是最重要的。」「希望不要把老年人扔在信息时代后面，毕竟我们以后也会老啊，也会有跟不上时代的那一天。」</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357581" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-1.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-1.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-1-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-1-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-1-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4>John Lewis 圣诞广告：《Give a Little Love》</h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1381361" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/john-lewis-christmas-advert-7-1605252671.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/john-lewis-christmas-advert-7-1605252671.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/john-lewis-christmas-advert-7-1605252671-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/john-lewis-christmas-advert-7-1605252671-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/john-lewis-christmas-advert-7-1605252671-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<p>时长：2:00</p>
<p>今年，John Lewis 和八位艺术家联手，采用了真人表演、动画、黏土等多种表现形式，讲述了一个关于「善意」的故事。John Lewis 表示，这个主题很符合「我们当下的感受」。</p>
<p><iframe src="https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=b3203smzj4l" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" data-mce-fragment="1"></iframe></p>
