➜同样 10000 元，有人买 iPhone 12 Pro Max，我却选 iPhone 12 mini + iPad Air 4
https://www.ifanr.com/1379807?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=	33755
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1379813" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03728.jpg" alt="" width="1494" height="996" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03728.jpg 1494w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03728-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03728-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03728-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1494px) 100vw, 1494px" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">iPhone 12 Pro Max 和 mini 发售时，这两款产品引起了大众超高关注。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 不过由于 iPhone 12 Pro Max 6.7 英寸屏幕加直角边框设计，不少人选择时犯了难，买吧，对部分人来讲确实不好单手握持，买 6.1 英寸的 iPhone 12 吧，大屏体验没有 6.7 英寸那么好。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 于是，一个让不少人跃跃欲试的解决方案出现了 —— <strong>买一部 iPhone 12 mini ，搭配着 10.9 英寸的 iPad Air 4 使用，这样「大小」可以兼顾</strong>。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 我就这样做了，体验可以用痛并快乐着来形容。</span></p>
<h3 class="ql-long-24360693" data-header="1"><span class="ql-author-24360693">iPhone 12 Pro Max ≈ 12 mini + iPad Air ？</span></h3>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">对我来讲，如果同时使用多台设备，iPhone 至少要 128GB 起步才够用，64GB 的 iPad 也暂时够用，于是我选择的是 iPhone 12 mini（128GB/5999 元）+ iPad Air（64GB/4799 元）+ Apple Pencil（二代/969 元），<strong>总价是 11767 元</strong>。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1379814" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03723-1.jpg" alt="" width="1669" height="1113" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03723-1.jpg 1669w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03723-1-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03723-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03723-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1669px) 100vw, 1669px" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 如果单独使用一台设备，iPhone 12 Pro Max 必须要 256GB 才能满足我的需求，价格为 10099 元。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 两个方案相比，差额是 1688 元，大约等于 1 个手办，5 顿聚餐，35 杯星巴克。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 不过一想到 1 变 3，这 1688 元还是挺值得的……好吧，我承认我在自我心理安慰。</span></p>
<h3 class="ql-long-24360693" data-header="1"><strong><span class="ql-author-24360693">iPhone 12 mini 实际体验怎么样？</span></strong></h3>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1379880" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03787.jpg" alt="" width="1655" height="1103" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03787.jpg 1655w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03787-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03787-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03787-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1655px) 100vw, 1655px" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">想买 iPhone 12 mini 的用户可能有三个心理难关过不去：5.4 英寸的屏幕够用吗，2227mAh 电池够用吗，直角边框硌手吗？</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><strong class="ql-author-24360693">（1）5.4 英寸的屏幕够用吗</strong></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 如果按长方形计算且不考虑「刘海」区域，6.1 英寸屏幕的显示面积为 139.77mm * 64.58mm = 9026.35（mm^2)，5.4 英寸屏幕的显示面积为 124.96mm * 57.67mm = 7206.44（mm^2）。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1379818" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/mini5.png" alt="" width="1360" height="1032" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/mini5.png 1360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/mini5-360x273.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/mini5-768x583.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/mini5-1024x777.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1360px) 100vw, 1360px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ iPhone 12 mini CAD 数据. 图片来自：某知情人士（知乎）</p>
</div>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 理论上，iPhone 12 mini 屏幕面积是 iPhone 11/12/Pro 的 79% 左右。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 实际体验中，iPhone 12 mini 的内容显示也是 iPhone 11 的 80% 左右，而游戏界面是等比例缩放的，没有缩小视觉范围。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1379881" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03781.jpg" alt="" width="1800" height="1200" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03781.jpg 1800w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03781-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03781-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03781-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 左：iPhone 12 mini。右：iPhone 11。因两部手机都贴了膜，可能会影响屏幕色温和显示效果</p>
</div>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><strong class="ql-author-24360693">（2）2227mAh 电池够用吗？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 早上 8:15 满电 100% 出门，打开自动 5G、WiFi 和蓝牙，匹配了 Apple Watch 和 AirPods Pro，中途按照日常使用习惯，不充电，晚上 8:30 的时候，iPhone 12 mini 剩余电量为  13%。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380326" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/mini10-1.png" alt="" width="1114" height="1048" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/mini10-1.png 1114w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/mini10-1-360x339.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/mini10-1-768x722.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/mini10-1-1024x963.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1114px) 100vw, 1114px" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 我的公司和家里随时都可以充电，外出习惯性带充电宝，这个续航时间对我来讲属于「可以接受但希望更好」的范围。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><strong class="ql-author-24360693">（3）直角边框硌手吗？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 硌手，尤其是对于习惯了圆角弧度边框的人来说。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 即使是 iPhone 12 mini 这么小的机身，握在手里也有非常明显的棱角感，不过远远算不上难受。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1379824" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03730.jpg" alt="" width="1339" height="893" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03730.jpg 1339w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03730-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03730-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03730-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1339px) 100vw, 1339px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 用习惯了圆角弧度边框，握持 iPhone 12 mini 需要一定适应时间，但大约 130g 的重量足以让人忘记直角边框</p>
</div>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 为了缓解握持感受问题，我搭配了苹果官方的皮革磁吸手机壳，手感确实提升不少，有种回到 iPhone 5 时代的感觉。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1379825" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03735.jpg" alt="" width="1800" height="1200" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03735.jpg 1800w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03735-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03735-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03735-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 苹果近期推出了 iPhone 12 配件搭配页面，我在文章《<a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/73gy52YJ2jrEZKI3IEZaqQ">苹果上线的 iPhone 12 配件搭配页面，让双十一「套路节」颜面扫地</a>》评论区放了链接，大家可以进去体验。</span></p>
<h3 class="ql-long-24360693" data-header="1"><strong><span class="ql-author-24360693">iPhone 12 拍照录像怎么样？</span></strong></h3>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">一句话总结，和 iPhone 12 配置一样，水准一样，成效质量一样，这里不再展开细说，大家可以看看样张。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1379829" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/IMG_0102.jpg" alt="" width="3024" height="4032" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/IMG_0102.jpg 3024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/IMG_0102-360x480.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/IMG_0102-768x1024.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 3024px) 100vw, 3024px" /></p>
<div data-header="1"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1379831" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/IMG_0129.jpg" alt="" width="4032" height="3024" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/IMG_0129.jpg 4032w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/IMG_0129-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/IMG_0129-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/IMG_0129-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 4032px) 100vw, 4032px" /></div>
<div data-header="1"></div>
