<p>▲ 超广角镜头也支持了夜景模式</p>
</div>
</div>
<div data-header="1"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1379838" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/IMG_0087.jpg" alt="" width="4032" height="3024" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/IMG_0087.jpg 4032w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/IMG_0087-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/IMG_0087-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/IMG_0087-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 4032px) 100vw, 4032px" /></div>
