<p>▲ 由于图片格式转化和压缩，照片的质感可能受到一定影响​</p>
</div>
</div>
<h3 class="ql-long-24360693" data-header="1"><strong><span class="ql-author-24360693">12 mini 和 iPad Air 4 搭配着用，是一种怎样的体验？</span></strong></h3>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">实施这个方案前，我做了一些使用场景的细分，让 iPhone 12 mini 和 iPad Air 4 承担不同的需求。</span></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1379890" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/mini9.png" alt="" width="1094" height="984" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/mini9.png 1094w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/mini9-360x324.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/mini9-768x691.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/mini9-1024x921.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1094px) 100vw, 1094px" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 体验下来，这套搭配方法优缺点都很明显，我们先来说说优点：</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><strong class="ql-author-24360693">（1）手机的便利性得到充分发挥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 打电话、发微信、拍照录影和扫码付款这几个动作变得更方便了，从口袋里掏出 iPhone 12 mini 单手操作没有压力，手机放回口袋里也「轻若无物」。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><strong class="ql-author-24360693">（2）短视频互动和「重游戏」体验再上一个台阶</strong></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 看抖音或者 B 站的时候，我用 iPhone 12 mini，「想刷就刷」，在评论区和人互撕或者发弹幕非常方便，一只手解决，怼人效率直线上升。</span></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1379871" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/IMG_89791.gif" alt="" width="270" height="480" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 很久没有用过能一只手操控的手机了</p>
</div>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 玩王者荣耀或者吃鸡之类的「20 分钟轻游戏」，掏出手机随时可以匹配。</span>而看长视频，比如追剧或者看电影，哪怕 iPhone 12 Pro Max 屏幕材质更好，分辨率更细腻，也在 iPad Air 4 的 10.9 英寸屏幕前败下阵来。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1379848" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03751.jpg" alt="" width="1465" height="977" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03751.jpg 1465w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03751-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03751-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03751-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1465px) 100vw, 1465px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 影音体验还是「大的」香</p>
</div>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 玩仙剑奇侠传或者梦幻西游这样的「1 小时起步重游戏」，用 iPad Air 4 体验更好，更有沉浸感。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><strong class="ql-author-24360693">（3）iPad 可以用来无纸化学习、轻办公和照片视频编辑，这个是 iPhone 12 Pro Max 做不到的，也是多一台 iPad Air 4 最大的优势</strong></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 用 iPad Air 4 分屏背单词，记笔记，用 MarginNote 读书等等，可以极大提升学习效率。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1379854" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/IMG_282.png" alt="" width="3072" height="2388" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/IMG_282.png 3072w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/IMG_282-360x280.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/IMG_282-768x597.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/IMG_282-1024x796.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3072px) 100vw, 3072px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲  iPad + Apple Pencil + MarginNote</p>
</div>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 偶尔临时处理一下微信公众号后台，用 iPad Air 4 就可以了。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 我喜欢回看相片，拿着 iPad Air 4 来看照片和视频，有一种往事历历在目的感觉，很有代入感，还可以用相册编辑器微调，修图和简单的视频剪辑体验哪怕 6.7 英寸的屏幕也无法提供。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1379856" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03747.jpg" alt="" width="1519" height="1013" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03747.jpg 1519w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03747-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03747-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03747-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1519px) 100vw, 1519px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 在 iPad 上编辑图片或简单剪辑视频，体验大大超过 iPhone</p>
</div>
<h3 class="ql-long-24360693"><strong><span class="ql-author-24360693">再来说说说缺点</span></strong></h3>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><strong class="ql-author-24360693">（1）从此以后，随时背包</strong></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 除了临时外出，大部分时间我都需要背着一个包，用来存放 iPad Air 4。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 比如出门前，我要多一个思考过程：今天需要带 iPad Air 4 吗？</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 如果把 iPad Air 4 背出去了，又没用到，就觉得很「亏」。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><strong class="ql-author-24360693">（2）iPhone 12 mini 刷短视频，体验没有 6 英寸以上机型好</strong></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 如果用 iPad Air 4 来刷，又特别「压手」，刷不了一会就想放下。这个时候就会无比想念​ 6.1 英寸的屏幕。​</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><strong class="ql-author-24360693">（3）iPhone 的游戏体验下降</strong></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 虽说大部分游戏都做了适配，等比例缩小了各种视觉元素，但这对游戏操控的精细度要求更高了，手指会遮挡更多屏幕面积。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1379857" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03745.jpg" alt="" width="1555" height="1037" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03745.jpg 1555w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03745-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03745-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03745-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1555px) 100vw, 1555px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 动作幅度一大，手指就遮住了更多屏幕</p>
</div>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><strong class="ql-author-24360693">（4）用不了双卡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> iPhone 12 mini 大陆版是单卡设计，这意味着双卡用户还得再带一部手机，不过这应该不影响苹果安卓双机党用户。</span></p>
<h3 class="ql-long-24360693" data-header="1"><strong><span class="ql-author-24360693">12 mini + iPad Air ？慎重考虑</span></strong></h3>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1379813" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03728.jpg" alt="" width="1494" height="996" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03728.jpg 1494w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03728-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03728-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC03728-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1494px) 100vw, 1494px" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">几天体验下来，我觉得这个搭配方案更适合以下几种用户：</span></p>
<ol>
<li class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">追求极致小体积手机的用户，能接纳产品的客观缺点</span></li>
<li class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">不怎么在手机上影音娱乐的用户</span></li>
<li class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">随时能给手机充电的用户</span></li>
<li class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">同时有 iPhone + iPad 需求，又预算有限的用户</span></li>
<li class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">iOS 安卓双系统用户</span></li>
</ol>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 对于有大量影音娱乐需求的 iPhone 用户来说，iPhone 12/Pro/Pro Max 才是更适合的选择。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">「大小搭配」真香定律只适合真正符合自己需求的用户，做出决定前，一定要先考虑好哦。</span></p>
<div id="ifanr_profile" style="border:1px solid #ccc;font-size:14px;margin:27px auto;font-family:Arial;">
<div style="overflow:hidden"><a target="_blank" href="https://www.ifanr.com/author/zhuhai" style="color:#000;text-decoration:none;"></a>
<div style="text-align:left;line-height:23px;margin-left:80px">
<div style="padding:10px 10px 10px 0">
<div style="margin:0;font-size: 14px;"><strong><a target="_blank" href="https://www.ifanr.com/author/zhuhai" style="color:#000;text-decoration:none;">朱 海</a></strong>
</div>
<div style="font-size: 13px; line-height:20px;">三流方案策划者，二流出镜主持人，一流败家浪荡侠</div>
</div>
